        <item>
            <title>v1.2</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>Pick your agent, per character</h3>
                <p>Bruce and Jazz can now each run a different AI provider. Click the title in any chat popover to switch between Claude, Codex, Copilot, Gemini, or OpenCode — or set them all at once from the menu bar. Unavailable providers are automatically detected and grayed out.</p>
                <h3>Fresh starts with /clear</h3>
                <p>Type /clear or hit the ↻ button to reset a conversation and start a new session instantly — no need to quit and relaunch.</p>
                <h3>Resize your agents</h3>
                <p>A new Size menu lets you switch between Large, Medium, and Small characters.</p>
                <h3>Multi-display fixes</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Characters no longer vanish when you click a secondary monitor</li>
                    <li>Dock detection now works when the Dock is pinned to the left or right, not just the bottom</li>
                    <li>Pinning characters to a specific display always keeps them visible</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>More providers</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Gemini support</li>
                    <li>OpenCode support</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2026 22:20:00 -0700</pubDate>
